HDBUr 'aShUr HYH 'aL-YUrMYHV M'aTh YHVH L'aMUr.
'yMD BSh'yUr BYTh YHVH VQUr'aTh ShM 'aTh-HDBUr HZH V'aMUrTh ShM'yV DBUr-YHVH KL- YHVDH HB'aYM BSh'yUrYM H'aLH LHShThChVTh LYHVH.
KH-'aMUr YHVH TShB'aVTh 'aLHY YShUr'aL HYTYBV DUrKYKM VM'yLLYKM V'aShKNH 'aThKM BMQVM HZH.
'aL-ThBTChV LKM 'aL-DBUrY HShQUr L'aMUr HYKL YHVH HYKL YHVH HYKL YHVH HMH.
KY 'aM-HYTYB ThYTYBV 'aTh-DUrKYKM V'aTh-M'yLLYKM 'aM-'yShV Th'yShV MShPhT BYN 'aYSh VBYN Ur'yHV.
GUr YThVM V'aLMNH L'a Th'yShQV VDM NQY 'aL-ThShPhKV BMQVM HZH V'aChUrY 'aLHYM 'aChUrYM L'a ThLKV LUr'y LKM.
VShKNThY 'aThKM BMQVM HZH B'aUrTSh 'aShUr NThThY L'aBVThYKM LMN-'yVLM V'yD- 'yVLM.
HNH 'aThM BTChYM LKM 'yL-DBUrY HShQUr LBLThY HV'yYL.
HGNB UrTShCh VN'aPh VHShB'y LShQUr VQTUr LB'yL VHLK 'aChUrY 'aLHYM 'aChUrYM 'aShUr L'a-YD'yThM.
VB'aThM V'yMDThM LPhNY BBYTh HZH 'aShUr NQUr'a-ShMY 'yLYV V'aMUrThM NTShLNV LM'yN 'yShVTh 'aTh KL-HThV'yBVTh H'aLH.
HM'yUrTh PhUrTShYM HYH HBYTh HZH 'aShUr-NQUr'a-ShMY 'yLYV B'yYNYKM GM 'aNKY HNH Ur'aYThY N'aM-YHVH.
KY LKV-N'a 'aL-MQVMY 'aShUr BShYLV 'aShUr ShKNThY ShMY ShM BUr'aShVNH VUr'aV 'aTh 'aShUr-'yShYThY LV MPhNY Ur'yTh 'yMY YShUr'aL.
V'yThH Y'yN 'yShVThKM 'aTh-KL-HM'yShYM H'aLH N'aM-YHVH V'aDBUr 'aLYKM HShKM VDBUr VL'a ShM'yThM V'aQUr'a 'aThKM VL'a 'yNYThM.
V'yShYThY LBYTh 'aShUr NQUr'a-ShMY 'yLYV 'aShUr 'aThM BTChYM BV VLMQVM 'aShUr- NThThY LKM VL'aBVThYKM K'aShUr 'yShYThY LShLV.
VHShLKThY 'aThKM M'yL PhNY K'aShUr HShLKThY 'aTh-KL-'aChYKM 'aTh KL-ZUr'y 'aPhUrYM.
V'aThH 'aL-ThThPhLL B'yD-H'yM HZH V'aL-ThSh'a B'yDM UrNH VThPhLH V'aL-ThPhG'y-BY KY-'aYNNY ShM'y 'aThK.
H'aYNK Ur'aH MH HMH 'yShYM B'yUrY YHVDH VBChTShVTh YUrVShLM.
HBNYM MLQTYM 'yTShYM VH'aBVTh MB'yUrYM 'aTh-H'aSh VHNShYM LShVTh BTShQ L'yShVTh KVNYM LMLKTh HShMYM VHSK NSKYM L'aLHYM 'aChUrYM LM'yN HK'ySNY.
H'aThY HM MK'ySYM N'aM-YHVH HLV'a 'aThM LM'yN BShTh PhNYHM.
LKN KH-'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH HNH 'aPhY VChMThY NThKTh 'aL-HMQVM HZH 'yL-H'aDM V'yL-HBHMH V'yL-'yTSh HShDH V'yL-PhUrY H'aDMH VB'yUrH VL'a ThKBH.
KH 'aMUr YHVH TShB'aVTh 'aLHY YShUr'aL 'yLVThYKM SPhV 'yL-ZBChYKM V'aKLV BShUr.
KY L'a-DBUrThY 'aTh-'aBVThYKM VL'a TShVYThYM BYVM HVTShY'a 'aVThM M'aUrTSh MTShUrYM 'yL-DBUrY 'yVLH VZBCh.
KY 'aM-'aTh-HDBUr HZH TShVYThY 'aVThM L'aMUr ShM'yV BQVLY VHYYThY LKM L'aLHYM V'aThM ThHYV-LY L'yM VHLKThM BKL-HDUrK 'aShUr 'aTShVH 'aThKM LM'yN YYTB LKM.
VL'a ShM'yV VL'a-HTV 'aTh-'aZNM VYLKV BM'yTShVTh BShUrUrVTh LBM HUr'y VYHYV L'aChVUr VL'a LPhNYM.
LMN-HYVM 'aShUr YTSh'aV 'aBVThYKM M'aUrTSh MTShUrYM 'yD HYVM HZH V'aShLCh 'aLYKM 'aTh-KL-'yBDY HNBY'aYM YVM HShKM VShLCh.
VLV'a ShM'yV 'aLY VL'a HTV 'aTh-'aZNM VYQShV 'aTh-'yUrPhM HUr'yV M'aBVThM.
VDBUrTh 'aLYHM 'aTh-KL-HDBUrYM H'aLH VL'a YShM'yV 'aLYK VQUr'aTh 'aLYHM VL'a Y'yNVKH.
V'aMUrTh 'aLYHM ZH HGVY 'aShUr LV'a-ShM'yV BQVL YHVH 'aLHYV VL'a LQChV MVSUr 'aBDH H'aMVNH VNKUrThH MPhYHM.
GZY NZUrK VHShLYKY VSh'aY 'yL-ShPhYM QYNH KY M'aS YHVH VYTSh 'aTh-DVUr 'yBUrThV.
KY-'yShV BNY-YHVDH HUr'y B'yYNY N'aVM-YHVH ShMV ShQVTShYHM BBYTh 'aShUr- NQUr'a-ShMY 'yLYV LTM'aV.
VBNV BMVTh HThPhTh 'aShUr BGY'a BN-HNM LShUrPh 'aTh-BNYHM V'aTh-BNThYHM B'aSh 'aShUr L'a TShVYThY VL'a 'yLThH 'yL-LBY.
LKN HNH-YMYM B'aYM N'aM-YHVH VL'a-Y'aMUr 'yVD HThPhTh VGY'a BN-HNM KY 'aM-GY'a HHUrGH VQBUrV BThPhTh M'aYN MQVM.
VHYThH NBLTh H'yM HZH LM'aKL L'yVPh HShMYM VLBHMTh H'aUrTSh V'aYN MChUrYD.
VHShBThY M'yUrY YHVDH VMChTShVTh YUrVShLM QVL ShShVN VQVL ShMChH QVL ChThN VQVL KLH KY LChUrBH ThHYH H'aUrTSh.
